SRE Meetup – Bangalore 

Talk 1: Building Multi-Cloud Reliable API Gateway Platforms
Takeaway: Multi-cloud is an SRE problem first, a platform problem second.

Talk 2: Inside the Biggest Outages – Hidden Failure Patterns Every SRE Should Know
Takeaway: Outages expose system design flaws, not individual mistakes.

Overall: Reliability is an architectural responsibility, not just an operational one.
